t require visas or passports to enter India (unless arriving from [[mainland China]], [[Hong Kong]], [[Macau]], [[Maldives]] or [[Pakistan]]), and may remain in the country without any limit of stay. Citizens of these countries may also live and work freely in India:<ref name=\"timatic\">{{Timatic Visa Policy|country=IN|accessdate=1 April 2017}}</ref>\n{|style=\" {{border-radius|1em}} {{box-shadow|0.1em|0.1em|0.5em|rgba(0,0,0,0.75)}}; background-color: white; border: 1px solid white; padding: 5px;\"\n|- style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|\n* {{flag|Bhutan}}\n* {{flag|Nepal}}\n|\n|}\n\n==Overseas citizens of India/persons of Indian origin==\nForeign citizens possessing an [[Overseas Citizen of India]] registration certificate or holders of a [[Persons of Indian Origin Card]] are exempt from visa requirements, have the right of domicile in India and are allowed unlimited entries into India. Citizens of [[Afghanistan]], [[Bangladesh]], [[Bhutan]], [[mainland China]], [[Nepal]],  [[Pakistan]] and [[Sri Lanka]] are generally not entitled to hold Overseas Indian Citizenship.\n\n==Visa-free entry==\nFrom March 1979, citizens of {{flag|Maldives}} do not require visas to enter India for 90 days (unless arriving from [[mainland China]]).<ref name=\"timatic\"/>\n\nCitizens of {{flag|Bangladesh}} do require a visa but the visa fee is waived and not required\n\n== Visa on arrival ==\nCitizens of the following countries can apply for a visa on arrival (VOA) in [[Delhi]](NCT), [[Mumbai]], [[Kolkata]], [[Chennai]], [[Bengaluru]] or [[Hyderabad]]. The visa is issued for business, tourist, medical and conference categories, and has a validity of 60 days.<ref>{{cite news |title=Visa-on-arrival for Japanese citizens from tomorrow|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Visa-on-arrival-for-Japanese-citizens-from-tomorrow/articleshow/51196223.cms|website=The Times of India|accessdate=12 July 2016}}</ref><ref>[https://www.touristvisaonline.com/india-visa]</ref> The cost is [[Indian rupee|\u20b9]]2,000.  This facility is not available to citizens if they or either of their parents or grandparents (paternal or maternal) was born in or is a permanent resident of Pakistan. The citizen should not have Pakistani origin or parents,grandparents or great grandparent from Pakistan<big>.</big> The VOA facility can be used for no more than two times in a calendar year.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mha1.nic.in/pdfs/visaarrivaljapanesenationals_22012016.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306222312/http://mha1.nic.in/pdfs/visaarrivaljapanesenationals_22012016.pdf|url-status=dead|archive-date=6 March 2016|title=Visa-on-arrival for Japanese citizens|publisher=National Informatics Centre, Ministry of Electronics & IT|accessdate=17 September 2017}}</ref><ref name=\"timatic\"/> Alternatively, foreign citizens eligible for a VOA can apply for an [[Visa policy of India#e-Visa|e-Visa]] instead if they intend to enter the country through an airport or seaport not covered by the VOA scheme.\n{|style=\" {{border-radius|1em}} {{box-shadow|0.1em|0.1em|0.5em|rgba(0,0,0,0.75)}}; background-color: white; border: 1px solid white; padding: 5px;\"\n|- style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|\n*{{flag|Japan}} <small>(temporarily suspended)<ref>[https://indembassy-tokyo.gov.in/pdf/Notice%20_Temporary.pdf]</ref></small>\n*{{flag|South Korea}} <small>(temporarily suspended)<ref>[https://www.indembassyseoul.gov.in/page/bbbbbbbb/]</ref></small>\n*{{flag|United Arab Emirates}} <small>(temporarily suspended)<ref>[https://www.financialexpress.com/lifestyle/health/coronavirus-live-updates-coronavirus-latest-news-updates-on-coronavirus-in-india-symptoms-prevention-pune-delhi-bangalore-hyderabad/1893880/]</ref> <sup>1</sup>\n|\n|}\n\n<small>1 \u2013 Conditional; only applicable to UAE citizens if they had earlier obtained e-Visa or regular/paper visa for India.</small> <ref>https://indianvisaonline.gov.in/visa/visa-on-arrival.html</ref>\n\n== {{anchor|e-Tourist Visa}} e-Visa ==\n\n<imagemap>\nImage:India ETV.png|thumb|right|300px|This clickable map shows a list of airports that accept the e-Visa.\n\npoly 2504 2186 2549 2219 2586 2227 2643 2219 2714 2172 2742 2107 2729 2040 2692 1986 2614 1955 2563 1961 2544 1965 2490 2012 2465 2075 2471 2133 2490 2165 [[Sri Guru Ram Dass Jee International Airport|Amritsar]]\npoly 3083 3299 3115 3343 3184 3378 3268 3363 3313 3323 3341 3264 3338 3193 3297 3139 3254 3113 3207 3103 3154 3110 3108 3144 3082 3181 3071 3244 [[Delhi International Airport|Delhi]]\npoly 2644 3832 2656 3895 2703 3951 2773 3975 2847 3953 2900 3902 2913 3845 2910 3800 2892 3758 2859 3725 2821 3705 2783 3698 2746 3703 2707 3718 2671 3749 2651 3787 [[Jaipur Airport|Jaipur]]\npoly 1417 5440 1445 5496 1491 5529 1540 5538 1604 5528 1649 5494 1675 5455 1684 5386 1663 5326 1601 5277 1551 5270 1507 5276 1455 5298 1420 5356 1413 5415 [[Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel International Airport|Ahmedabad]]\npoly 1462 6782 1508 6833 1551 6853 1604 6856 1668 6834 1716 6767 1720 6700 1685 6632 1636 6595 1572 6589 1549 6592 1497 6620 1467 6649 1449 6702 1452 6750 [[Mumbai International Airport|Mumbai]]\npoly 1715 8186 1723 8234 1727 8256 1765 8303 1827 8334 1911 8322 1957 8282 1984 8220 1985 8169 1962 8110 1918 8079 1871 8064 1827 8065 1788 8076 1749 8105 1723 8152 [[Goa International Airport|Goa]]\npoly 3120 9012 3151 9095 3215 9139 3273 9141 3345 9113 3373 9084 3392 9029 3391 8992 3375 8941 3344 8900 3292 8877 3224 8876 3181 8896 3152 8918 3128 8959 [[Bengaluru International Airport|Bengaluru]]\npoly 2569 10157 2568 10196 2570 10222 2579 10259 2599 10286 2630 10317 2672 10333 2736 10331 2796 10293 2822 10251 2835 10215 2831 10165 2818 10133 2788 10097 2760 10074 2713 10063 2686 10064 2649 10072 2616 10094 2589 10121 [[Kochi International Airport|Kochi]]\npoly 2782 10876 2820 10924 2883 10952 2945 10947 2997 10916 3032 10865 3040 10824 3034 10773 3011 10731 2984 10706 2929 10680 2875 10687 2841 10699 2806 10721 2780 10758 2772 10796 2772 10843 [[Thiruvananthapuram International Airport|Thiruvananthapuram]]\npoly 3521 9993 3537 10046 3539 10054 3561 10086 3598 10111 3654 10122 3701 10113 3742 10094 3775 10058 3790 10017 3791 9965 3778 9927 3755 9892 3707 9856 3648 9854 3608 9863 3565 9884 3525 9943 [[Tiruchirappalli International Airport|Tiruchirappalli]]\npoly 4062 9118 4064 9172 4087 9214 4126 9255 4188 9276 4256 9265 4311 9218 4333 9146 4325 9097 4296 9041 4236 9011 4199 9002 4152 9014 4113 9031 4083 9064 [[Chennai International Airport|Chennai]]\npoly 3448 7533 3457 7595 3489 7640 3514 7665 3565 7682 3628 7678 3697 7628 3719 7563 3712 7497 3667 7441 3620 7415 3573 7410 3517 7428 3484 7452 3463 7487 [[Hyderabad International Airport|Hyderabad]]\npoly 6959 5404 6961 5471 6986 5514 7039 5558 7096 5565 7171 5543 7212 5495 7228 5433 7224 5394 7206 5355 7172 5317 7130 5297 7086 5295 7048 5303 7018 5313 6981 5348 [[Kolkata International Airport|Kolkata]]\npoly 5745 4680 5748 4723 5767 4768 5791 4799 5830 4823 5891 4830 5954 4806 5999 4764 6014 4707 6013 4669 5993 4620 5966 4583 5932 4560 5882 4559 5846 4560 5803 4585 5775 4598 5753 4638 [[Gaya Airport|Gaya]]\npoly 5002 4468 5005 4494 5034 4550 5079 4588 5126 4597 5178 4596 5239 4561 5264 4510 5273 4465 5274 4428 5251 4385 5218 4353 5175 4333 5147 4325 5097 4332 5052 4355 5021 4387 5006 4431 [[Lal Bahadur Shastri Airport|Varanasi]]\npoly 4403 3952 4432 4009 4469 4044 4517 4058 4583 4050 4650 4006 4673 3941 4668 3896 4650 3847 4612 3805 4540 3782 4484 3798 4442 3817 4420 3857 4404 3892 4398 3928 [[Chaudhary Charan Singh Airport|Lucknow]]\npoly 2982 2404 2986 2449 3001 2482 3025 2513 3069 2542 3130 2551 3176 2537 3231 2491 3251 2439 3251 2400 3243 2361 3222 2325 3174 2290 3128 2277 3090 2279 3049 2299 3019 2319 2990 2359 [[Chandigarh International Airport|Chandigarh]]\npoly 3651 6085 3680 6139 3721 6168 3769 6179 3809 6176 3874 6141 3905 6101 3918 6050 3908 5990 3890 5963 3857 5932 3822 5915 3784 5910 3751 5910 3721 5920 3687 5941 3665 5975 3651 6006 3646 6051 [[Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar International Airport|Nagpur]]\npoly 1756 7055 1763 7090 1789 7137 1831 7166 1868 7180 1917 7177 1959 7161 1986 7138 2017 7099 2025 7066 2024 7031 2016 6990 1992 6955 1966 6931 1935 6913 1903 6909 1858 6911 1820 6927 1785 6957 1762 6990 1754 7038 [[Pune Airport|Pune]]\npoly 2073 9169 2107 9197 2134 9210 2182 9219 2247 9202 2285 9168 2311 9116 2311 9068 2301 9024 2279 8989 2249 8965 2208 8949 2162 8949 2112 8962 2079 8989 2049 9040 2044 9100 2054 9139 [[Mangaluru Airport|Mangaluru]]\npoly 2456 9863 2471 9902 2497 9940 2527 9956 2578 9972 2624 9967 2676 9943 2711 9892 2724 9851 2720 9809 2708 9778 2690 9745 2652 9717 2613 9705 2577 9702 2541 9710 2512 9725 2476 9761 2459 9798 2451 9834 [[Calicut International Airport|Kozhikode]]\npoly 2934 9873 2940 9907 2955 9941 2978 9968 3007 9987 3038 9997 3090 9998 3145 9977 3176 9945 3194 9908 3202 9875 3197 9822 3175 9779 3134 9747 3096 9733 3053 9726 2992 9751 2961 9778 2934 9827 [[Coimbatore International Airport|Coimbatore]]\npoly 6830 3904 6825 3935 6829 3969 6844 4004 6868 4038 6904 4060 6949 4072 7010 4061 7040 4045 7068 4017 7091 3978 7095 3939 7092 3899 7078 3862 7054 3836 7022 3815 6989 3804 6946 3800 6910 3811 6878 3827 6849 3858 [[Bagdogra Airport|Bagdogra]]\npoly 7974 4106 7993 4145 8024 4176 8060 4192 8114 4201 8163 4188 8210 4146 8230 4112 8238 4072 8234 4028 8221 3993 8197 3966 8170 3946 8132 3931 8095 3928 8065 3934 8027 3952 8006 3967 7987 3992 7974 4016 7966 4057 [[Lokpriya Gopinath Bordoloi International Airport|Guwahati]]\npoly 5273 7164 5318 7164 5350 7175 5379 7189 5400 7209 5417 7237 5429 7267 5434 7288 5433 7315 5427 7345 5410 7375 5395 7395 5368 7417 5339 7430 5309 7437 5301 7436 5276 7435 5245 7427 5232 7420 5223 7416 5210 7405 5194 7392 5182 7375 5174 7359 5166 7334 5159 7314 5159 7289 5163 7263 5178 7230 5191 7211 5216 7189 5237 7177 5263 7168 [[Visakhapatnam Airport|Visakhapatnam]]\npoly 3295 10216 3290 10228 3288 10237 3284 10249 3282 10263 3281 10268 3281 10274 3280 10283 3283 10296 3284 10306 3286 10318 3290 10325 3292 10333 3298 10348 3305 10355 3317 10371 3324 10378 3335 10387 3341 10395 3355 10402 3370 10407 3381 10411 3400 10415 3417 10416 3437 10413 3456 10411 3474 10403 3486 10398 3502 10386 3512 10377 3521 10367 3532 10351 3537 10341 3543 10329 3547 10322 3551 10307 3551 10301 3551 10293 3551 10281 3551 10271 3552 10258 3548 10249 3545 10236 3538 10224 3534 10212 3528 10201 3519 10194 3517 10189 3510 10182 3504 10176 3498 10172 3488 10164 3478 10159 3467 10154 3450 10148 3432 10145 3414 10144 3407 10143 3388 10148 3374 10151 3357 10157 3338 10169 3323 10179 3305 10196 3297 10214 3297 10215 [[Madurai Airport|Madurai]]\npoly 6063 6408 6074 6424 6085 6441 6097 6453 6103 6461 6120 6470 6135 6477 6155 6485 6170 6487 6186 6489 6204 6488 6222 6484 6240 6481 6252 6470 6264 6465 6277 6457 6290 6446 6299 6429 6305 6420 6315 6406 6319 6392 6322 6381 6322 6368 6323 6350 6323 6338 6322 6328 6320 6321 6316 6306 6311 6294 6305 6285 6300 6274 6292 6263 6271 6246 6261 6234 6246 6229 6234 6223 6208 6218 6199 6217 6193 6215 6179 6217 6162 6220 6147 6222 6125 6229 6105 6244 6093 6253 6082 6262 6077 6274 6064 6291 6059 6312 6054 6334 6052 6350 6051 6365 6054 6384 6059 6401 6061 6406 [[Biju Patnaik Airport|Bhubaneswar]]\npoly 8794 9508 8799 9524 8806 9536 8815 9545 8826 9558 8833 9564 8842 9570 8848 9576 8853 9578 8860 9581 8868 9584 8877 9589 8890 9592 8899 9594 8912 9595 8923 9595 8932 9595 8943 9595 8961 9590 8974 9585 8990 9579 9002 9569 9017 9559 9026 9544 9033 9534 9040 9522 9047 9507 9052 9495 9054 9484 9056 9466 9056 9457 9054 9440 9047 9409 9034 9385 9020 9367 9001 9351 8992 9345 8978 9336 8965 9332 8941 9326 8919 9322 8897 9324 8876 9332 8857 9339 8842 9346 8831 9355 8816 9372 8804 9386 8801 9396 8789 9427 8787 9443 8786 9463 8787 9483 8787 9479 [[Veer Savarkar International Airport|Port Blair]]\n</imagemap>\n\nOn 27 November 2014, the Electronic Travel Authorisation (ETA) facility became operational for citizens of over 40 eligible countries, including those who are eligible for visa on arrival. The list was further expanded to 113 countries in August 2015 (see chart below).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pib.nic.in/newsite/PrintRelease.aspx?relid=124631|title=Government extends e-Tourist Visa scheme to 36 more countries and 7 more airports from August 15, 2015|website=pib.nic.in|accessdate=17 September 2017}}</ref> ETA is issued for tourism, visiting friends and family, short duration medical treatment and business visits. The scheme was renamed to e-Tourist Visa (eTV) on 15 April 2015.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ndtv.com/india-news/government-changes-name-of-visa-on-arrival-scheme-to-e-tourist-visa-754929|title=Government Changes Name of Visa on Arrival Scheme to E-Tourist Visa|publisher=NDTV |accessdate=17 September 2017}}</ref> On 1 April 2017 the scheme was renamed e-Visa with three subcategories: e-Tourist Visa, e-Business Visa and e-Medical Visa.\n\nAn application for e-Visa must be made at least four calendar days in advance of the date of arrival and can be made as early as 120 days in advance. The visa is valid for one year from the date of arrival. Continuous stay during each visit on an e-tourist visa must not exceed 90 days, except for citizens of Canada, Japan, United Kingdom and United States as well as all nationalities visiting on an e-business visa who are allowed to stay for 180 days.<ref>[https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/e-visa-validity-for-tourist-and-business-goes-up-from-60-days-to-1-year/story-IENJYD8b54EeFvVTtCL6GM.html e-visa validity for tourist and business goes up from 60 days to 1 year]</ref> The duration of stay cannot be extended.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indianvisaonline.gov.in/evisa/tvoa.html|title=Indian e-Visa|website=indianvisaonline.gov.in|accessdate=17 September 2017}}</ref> The e-Visa fees are divided into four slabs of zero, US$25, US$80 and US$100, depending on nationality (based on [[Reciprocity (international relations)|reciprocity]]; see table below and notes), plus a bank fee of 2.5% of the visa fee.<ref name=\"e-Tourist Visa Fee\">{{cite web|url=https://indianvisaonline.gov.in/evisa/eTV_revised_fee_final.pdf|title=Country/Territory Wise e-Tourist Visa Fee|publisher=Bureau of Immigration, Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India |accessdate=28 June 2018}}</ref>\n\ne-Visa allows arrival at the following 28 airports and 5 seaports:<ref>{{cite web|url=https://indianvisaonline.gov.in/visa/tvoa.html|title=JSP Page|website=indianvisaonline.gov.in|accessdate=17 September 2017}}</ref>\n\n'''Airports'''\n\n{|\n|\n*[[Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel International Airport|Ahmedabad]]\n*[[Sri Guru Ram Dass Jee International Airport|Amritsar]]\n*[[Bagdogra Airport|Bagdogra]]\n*[[Bengaluru International Airport|Bengaluru]]\n*[[Biju Patnaik Airport|Bhubaneswar]]<ref>[https://www.aninews.in/news/national/general-news/fillip-to-odisha-tourism-biju-patnaik-international-airport-gets-e-visa-counter20190121194909/]</ref>\n*[[Chandigarh International Airport|Chandigarh]]\n|valign=top|\n*[[Chennai International Airport|Chennai]]\n*[[Coimbatore International Airport|Coimbatore]]\n*[[Delhi International Airport|Delhi]]\n*[[Gaya Airport|Gaya]]\n*[[Goa International Airport|Goa]]\n*[[Lokpriya Gopinath Bordoloi International Airport|Guwahati]]\n|valign=top|\n*[[Hyderabad International Airport|Hyderabad]]\n*[[Jaipur Airport|Jaipur]]\n*[[Cochin International Airport|Kochi]]\n*[[Kannur International Airport|Kannur]]\n*[[Kolkata International Airport|Kolkata]]\n*[[Calicut International Airport|Kozhikode]]\n*[[Chaudhary Charan Singh International Airport|Lucknow]]\n|valign=top|\n*[[Madurai Airport|Madurai]]\n*[[Mangaluru Airport|Mangaluru]]\n*[[Mumbai International Airport|Mumbai]]\n*[[Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar International Airport|Nagpur]]\n*[[Pune Airport|Pune]]\n*[[Veer Savarkar International Airport|Port Blair]]\n|valign=top|\n*[[Thiruvananthapuram International Airport|Thiruvananthapuram]]\n*[[Tiruchirappalli International Airport|Tiruchirappalli]]\n*[[Lal Bahadur Shastri Airport|Varanasi]]\n*[[Visakhapatnam Airport|Visakhapatnam]]\n|\n|}\n\n'''Seaports'''\n\n{|\n|\n*[[Cochin Port|Cochin]]\n*[[Mormugao|Goa]]\n*[[New Mangalore Port|Mangalore]]\n*[[Mumbai Port|Mumbai]]\n*[[Chennai Port|Chennai]]\n|\n|}\n\nExit is possible via any authorized immigration check post.\n\nCitizens of the following countries and territories who hold ordinary passports are eligible to obtain the e-Visa (unless the citizen is of [[Pakistani people|Pakistani origin]]):<ref name=evisa>{{cite web | url=https://indianvisaonline.gov.in/visa/tvoa.html | title=e-TOURIST VISA (eTV) | author=Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India | publisher=National Informatics Centre | location=India |accessdate=19 June 2019}}</ref>\n\n{|style=\" {{border-radius|1em}} {{box-shadow|0.1em|0.1em|0.5em|rgba(0,0,0,0.75)}}; background-color: white; border: 1px solid white; padding: 5px;\"\n|- style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|\n*{{flagicon|European Union|}} All [[European Union citizenship|European Union citizens]]\n*{{flag|Albania}}\n*{{flag|Andorra}}\n*{{flag|Angola}}\n*{{flag|Antigua and Barbuda}}\n*{{flag|Argentina}}<sup>3</sup>\n*{{flag|Armenia}}\n*{{flag|Australia}}\n*{{flag|Azerbaijan}}\n*{{flag|Bahamas}}\n*{{flag|Barbados}}\n*{{flag|Belarus}}\n*{{flag|Belize}}\n*{{flag|Benin}}\n*{{flag|Bolivia}}\n*{{flag|Bosnia and Herzegovina}}\n*{{flag|Botswana}}\n*{{flag|Brazil}}\n*{{flag|Brunei}}\n*{{flag|Burundi}}\n*{{flag|Cambodia}}\n*{{flag|Cameroon}}\n*{{flag|Canada}}\n*{{flag|Cape Verde}}\n*{{flag|Chile}}\n*{{flag|China}}\n*{{flag|Colombia}}\n*{{flag|Comoros}}\n*{{flag|Costa Rica}}\n*{{flag|Cuba}}\n*{{flag|Djibouti}}\n*{{flag|Dominica}}\n*{{flag|Dominican Republic}}\n*{{flag|Ecuador}}\n*{{flag|El Salvador}}\n|valign=top|\n*{{flag|Eritrea}}\n*{{flag|Eswatini}}\n*{{flag|Fiji}}<sup>3</sup>\n*{{flag|Gabon}}\n*{{flag|Gambia}}\n*{{flag|Georgia}}\n*{{flag|Ghana}}\n*{{flag|Grenada}}\n*{{flag|Guatemala}}\n*{{flag|Guinea}}\n*{{flag|Guyana}}\n*{{flag|Haiti}}\n*{{flag|Honduras}}\n*{{f